title: CRUDE MIX I 52 - SZCH
description:
â€œFor CRUDE's 52nd edition one of the infamous Low Income $quad co-founders steps in like a whirlwind.

title: VOLTA P009 - SZCH
description:
â€œUnarguably the most respected artist weâ€™ve had on the roster so far, SZCHâ€™s original take on house music and his unabashedly flamboyant stylistics have brought him worldwide acclaim - with multiple international releases and a couple of under-the-table YouTube/vinyl hits in his cookbook, he is one of the protagonists of the contemporary spin on lo-fi aesthetic, as well as Croatiaâ€™s dance music gemstone.

Aside from DJing and producing he has - as one third of low income $quad records - curated a number of standout experimental tape compilations in LP/EP format, contributing to Croatiaâ€™s visibility on the global underground map, perhaps more so than any other local label.
For our ninth instalment, he forwards a live recording of his recent DJ set - a context that most completely represents the opulent tongue-in-cheek mythology of SZCH.â€
